{"id":277943,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/维权网-刘沙沙等多位维权人士在全国人大信访办/","date":"2013-02-05T12:30:42Z","modified":"2013-02-05T12:30:42Z","title":"维权网 | 刘沙沙等多位维权人士在全国人大信访办门口拉横幅抗议刑诉法绑架窃听条款（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>（维权网信息员李军报道）</span>2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日下午</span><span>，刘沙沙等多位维权人士们在北京永定门西街甲一号、全国人大信访办门口拉起横幅，呼吁要求新刑诉法取消“绑架条款”，限制“窃听条款”。</span></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>刘沙沙表示，此前自己和其它维权人士一起，向最高法院提交刑诉法建议书，要求废除不通知家属之绑架条款，废除不公布证人姓名之密证条款；限制技术侦察之窃听条款。最高法院的法官们对刘沙沙的答复是“送材料可以，不要叫上别人一起来。用意见来说服我们，不要那种行动。”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>刘沙沙认为，刑诉法绑架条款是公安国安检察院多年努力的结果，我一个人来送意见书，这一个人，这几张纸，如何抵得过公安部国安部检察院三家机关的力量？法官们要我邮寄，不要上门送，尤其不要叫上其他人。我认为社会对一个问题获得正确认识，得靠多元的力量。刑诉法通过，就是法院人大被公安国安的资料给淹没了。老百姓能收集的证据和法理根本比不上公安国安检察院三大机关，我们必须通过行动唤醒大家，提供更多相反的资料，让人大、法院认识社会生活的另一方面。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>反对刑诉法绑架条款签字名单：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>翟社利，陕西宝鸡，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15801455248 </span><span>李美青</span><span> </span><span>丰台区石榴庄</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 13124734318</span><span>。许高为</span><span> </span><span>辽宁省道教道士</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 13146125029</span><span>。张爱</span><span> </span><span>北京房山区</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 13161885992</span><span>。闫森</span><span> </span><span>湖北荆门市</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 13277663168</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>阮积忠</span><span> </span><span>湖北省荆州市</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 15110014491</span><span>，郭红</span><span> </span><span>湖北省荆州市</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 15652115855</span><span>，李焕君</span><span> </span><span>北京丰台</span><span> </span><span>石榴庄</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 13439265647</span><span>，张金保</span><span> </span><span>上海市静安区</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 13524365285</span><span>，李国谅</span><span> </span><span>北京大兴</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 13661235688</span><span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>黄玲</span><span> </span><span>湖北省武汉市</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 13261919066</span><span>。常卫云</span><span> </span><span>河南新乡</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 15639907185 </span><span>张群翔</span><span> </span><span>山东省招远市</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 15600244282</span><span>，徐香玉</span><span> </span><span>北京大兴</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 13691303056</span><span>，林明洁</span><span> </span><span>辽宁省</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 13264353512</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>刘华琼</span><span> </span><span>湖北</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 13911468798 </span><span>邹四新</span><span> </span><span>湖北</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 15010569778</span><span>，张憬民</span><span> </span><span>北京市</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 010 86935770</span><span>，王全宗</span><span> </span><span>河南洛阳</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 15544213472</span><span>，张海彦</span><span> </span><span>辽宁省</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 15942886211</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>朱萍萍，上海，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13585854650</span><span>。兰桂媛，湖南岳阳，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15200313428</span><span>。王桂香，吉林省，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13943370976</span><span>。于艳华，江苏徐州</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-cgHMa0ciAB0/URDzEFbT2ZI/AAAAAAAAbfM/IcCgyioInqE/s1600/%E5%8F%8D%E5%AF%B9%E7%BB%91%E6%9E%B6%E6%9D%A1%E6%AC%BE.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"225\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-cgHMa0ciAB0/URDzEFbT2ZI/AAAAAAAAbfM/IcCgyioInqE/s320/%E5%8F%8D%E5%AF%B9%E7%BB%91%E6%9E%B6%E6%9D%A1%E6%AC%BE.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>感谢维权人士刘沙沙提供的现场图片</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-UA959TwBH1A/URDzGM0g-lI/AAAAAAAAbfU/wFs21b